  "code": "```python\nimport json\n\ndef remove_duplicates_while_preserving_order(input_list):\n    unique_elements = {}\n    output_list = []\n    for element in input_list:\n        if element not in unique_elements:\n            unique_elements[element] = True\n            output_list.append(element)\n    return json.dumps(output_list)\n```",
