  "approach": "To check if a string is a palindrome after ignoring spaces, punctuation, and case, we can follow these steps:",
  "code": "```python\nimport re\n\ndef is_palindrome(s):\n    s = re.sub(r'[^a-zA-Z0-9]', '', s).lower()\n    return s == s[::-1]\n```",
